Slice Prep:

1. Vibratome E0.501 error

The manual describes E0.5xx errors as being related to the light barrier inside the vibratome, and suggest turning off and calling a Leica technician.
Dan Gill found this youtube video ( ) which provides instructions for how to correct the error.
This should be tried before calling a Leica technician, but do not perform fixes beyond those that are strightforward, as it could void the warranty on the vibratome.

